  "texts": [
    "To take advantage of transfer learning with a pre-trained ViT, the 3D data from a plane were split into a 2D slice array.",
    "The problem with slice-based approaches such as CNN is that they fail to retain the dependencies of associated features between slices.",
    "To overcome this problem, the sequence classification task uses a time series classification with a transformer.",
    "Another alternative is to use 3D deep models; however, transfer learning with a pre-trained 3D is not currently available.",
    "Therefore, these approaches do not generalize well when trained on insufficient data."
